00:12:09,270 --> 00:12:10,320
I'll definitely be stricter

298
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:13,030
with Miao than I was with you
when you were little.

299
00:12:13,480 --> 00:12:14,200
Alright, then.

300
00:12:19,270 --> 00:12:20,360
Our main focus right now

301
00:12:20,510 --> 00:12:21,870
is on tech-related toys.

302
00:12:22,150 --> 00:12:24,670
They can help develop
children's cognitive skills

303
00:12:24,870 --> 00:12:26,510
and even support social interaction.

304
00:12:26,630 --> 00:12:27,320
We also pay

305
00:12:27,320 --> 00:12:28,000
close attention

306
00:12:28,080 --> 00:12:29,480
to our brand image now,

307
00:12:29,510 --> 00:12:31,510
and we've already established

308
00:12:31,670 --> 00:12:33,120
a very good reputation in China.

309
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:34,670
I believe we will achieve

310
00:12:34,790 --> 00:12:36,510
even better results in the future.

311
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:38,630
That's Meow Meow Toys'

312
00:12:38,750 --> 00:12:40,080
strategic plan for the future.

313
00:12:40,320 --> 00:12:41,600
Now, please allow me

314
00:12:41,790 --> 00:12:42,670
to share a story.

315
00:12:42,960 --> 00:12:44,550
Last year, we received

316
00:12:44,630 --> 00:12:45,670
a special letter.

317
00:12:45,870 --> 00:12:47,360
An autistic child

318
00:12:47,840 --> 00:12:48,790
uttered his first words

319
00:12:48,790 --> 00:12:49,840
after playing

320
00:12:50,360 --> 00:12:51,550
with our interactive

321
00:12:51,750 --> 00:12:52,480
parent-child toys.

322
00:12:52,750 --> 00:12:54,120
And that made us believe even more

323
00:12:54,440 --> 00:12:56,720
that toys aren't just plain products,

324
00:12:56,960 --> 00:12:59,120
but keys to the world.

325
00:13:28,080 --> 00:13:28,720
Shuchun,

326
00:13:29,910 --> 00:13:31,550
it's a good day today.

327
00:13:32,790 --> 00:13:33,720
Meow Meow Toys

328
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:37,440
is going to be listed
on the Shenzhen Stock Exchange.

329
00:13:38,200 --> 00:13:39,840
Wanzhi asked me
to ring the bell together,

330
00:13:42,240 --> 00:13:43,510
but I refused.

331
00:13:44,270 --> 00:13:46,120
All the senior executives declined,

332
00:13:46,790 --> 00:13:48,200
wanting to give this honor

333
00:13:48,840 --> 00:13:50,270
to their colleagues.

334
00:13:51,240 --> 00:13:52,030
In the end,

335
00:13:54,480 --> 00:13:55,840
I was chosen again

336
00:13:57,750 --> 00:13:58,790
with the most votes.

337
00:13:59,750 --> 00:14:00,480
Therefore,

338
00:14:01,270 --> 00:14:02,630
today, I,

339
00:14:03,510 --> 00:14:05,120
your wife, Li Juan,

340
00:14:09,960 --> 00:14:10,440
am not going

341
00:14:10,550 --> 00:14:12,440
as a co-founder,

342
00:14:16,030 --> 00:14:16,670
but representing

343
00:14:16,840 --> 00:14:18,670
the ordinary working people.

344
00:14:24,270 --> 00:14:25,510
Zhou Shuchun,

345
00:14:27,200 --> 00:14:28,720
are you proud?

346
00:14:31,480 --> 00:14:32,960
Are you proud of me?

347
00:14:51,120 --> 00:14:52,480
When Meow Meow Toys

348
00:14:52,670 --> 00:14:54,240
appears on the big screen,

349
00:14:55,270 --> 00:14:57,030
I remember the afternoon
twenty years ago,

350
00:14:57,510 --> 00:14:59,480
when I squatted in the canteen
peeling potatoes.

351
00:15:00,480 --> 00:15:01,600
Back then,

352
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:03,270
though I was at the bottom,

353
00:15:03,960 --> 00:15:05,000
I still had a dream,

354
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:08,030
a dream about creating
something beautiful.

355
00:15:08,750 --> 00:15:10,320
I've worked as a canteen helper,

356
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:12,000
hospital nurse,

357
00:15:12,720 --> 00:15:13,910
bar kitchen helper,

358
00:15:14,440 --> 00:15:15,720
hotel waitress,

359
00:15:16,080 --> 00:15:17,120
and factory worker.

360
00:15:17,720 --> 00:15:19,000
I've also run a stall in Dongmen

361
00:15:19,390 --> 00:15:20,630
to sell clothes.

362
00:15:21,360 --> 00:15:22,440
From the moment

363
00:15:22,750 --> 00:15:24,270
I first arrived in Shenzhen

364
00:15:24,630 --> 00:15:25,750
to the day

365
00:15:25,870 --> 00:15:27,630
I brought joy to others,

366
00:15:28,080 --> 00:15:28,870
I have walked

367
00:15:29,390 --> 00:15:29,960
this path

368
00:15:30,080 --> 00:15:32,320
for 9,365 days.

369
00:15:33,030 --> 00:15:33,840
Someone asked me

370
00:15:34,120 --> 00:15:35,600
why I named this company

371
00:15:35,840 --> 00:15:37,000
Meow Meow Toys.

372
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:40,120
Firstly, it's to commemorate
a cat that has been

373
00:15:40,240 --> 00:15:42,390
a companion to my friends
and me for many years.

374
00:15:42,670 --> 00:15:43,440
We named it

375
00:15:43,510 --> 00:15:44,360
"Little Friend"

376
00:15:44,750 --> 00:15:45,670
back then.

377
00:15:46,440 --> 00:15:48,030
On a deeper level,

378
00:15:48,600 --> 00:15:49,440
"Meow" represents

379
00:15:50,030 --> 00:15:52,390
the wonder of a child
seeing the world for the first time.

380
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:53,720
It also symbolizes

381
00:15:54,080 --> 00:15:56,240
the vitality that
pushes through hardship.

382
00:15:56,790 --> 00:15:57,630
It stands for

383
00:15:58,200 --> 00:16:00,320
the courage to keep moving forward,

384
00:16:00,960 --> 00:16:01,720
and also

385
00:16:02,480 --> 00:16:04,600
the deep‑rooted spirit
of the Chinese people.

386
00:16:05,910 --> 00:16:06,600
Once, we were

387
00:16:07,030 --> 00:16:08,150
only a manufacturer for

388
00:16:08,270 --> 00:16:09,030
international brands.

389
00:16:09,720 --> 00:16:10,360
But today,

390
00:16:10,870 --> 00:16:12,030
Meow Meow Toys

391
00:16:12,270 --> 00:16:14,000
brings original Chinese toys

392
00:16:14,240 --> 00:16:16,240
into the childhoods
of children worldwide,

393
00:16:17,080 --> 00:16:18,720
changing not only
the products themselves,

394
00:16:19,320 --> 00:16:20,790
but also marking the leap

395
00:16:21,120 --> 00:16:23,320
from "Made in China"
to "Created in China".

396
00:16:23,790 --> 00:16:24,360
This

397
00:16:24,510 --> 00:16:25,200
is our gift

398
00:16:25,320 --> 00:16:27,240
to the world.

399
00:16:51,320 --> 00:16:51,960
Right now,

400
00:16:52,750 --> 00:16:54,550
I want to say something
to my 20-year-old self.

401
00:16:56,320 --> 00:16:57,000
Hello, you.

402
00:16:58,150 --> 00:16:59,360
Clumsy and naive as you were.

403
00:16:59,840 --> 00:17:00,750
Don't give up.

404
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:02,910
With hard work,

405
00:17:03,960 --> 00:17:05,070
everything is possible.

406
00:17:05,830 --> 00:17:06,480
And I also

407
00:17:06,750 --> 00:17:08,640
want to tell everyone
who's chasing their dreams.

408
00:17:09,440 --> 00:17:10,790
Life is not a racetrack,

409
00:17:11,680 --> 00:17:12,510
but an open field.

410
00:17:13,030 --> 00:17:14,440
When you turn the impossible

411
00:17:14,830 --> 00:17:15,750
into the possible,

412
00:17:16,550 --> 00:17:19,030
the whole world will make way for you.

413
00:17:32,350 --> 00:17:34,030
The ordinary can harbor miracles.

414
00:17:34,550 --> 00:17:36,070
And a childlike heart
can change the world.

415
00:17:36,680 --> 00:17:39,200
Meow Meow Toys will always be there

416
00:17:39,440 --> 00:17:40,590
with children and adults

417
00:17:40,920 --> 00:17:41,830
around the world.

418
00:17:42,400 --> 00:17:44,070
Finally, please allow me to pay tribute

419
00:17:44,590 --> 00:17:46,070
to all who are rooted in the dust,

420
00:17:46,270 --> 00:17:47,550
yet still lift their eyes

421
00:17:48,310 --> 00:17:49,000
to the stars.

422
00:18:36,440 --> 00:18:37,070
Ms. Fang...

423
00:20:08,310 --> 00:20:08,830
Ms. Fang.

424
00:20:08,960 --> 00:20:09,480
Xue?

425
00:20:09,550 --> 00:20:10,270
They're inside.

426
00:20:14,880 --> 00:20:15,960
Good girl, Miao.

427
00:20:16,550 --> 00:20:18,160
Recite it to me again.

428
00:20:19,590 --> 00:20:22,270
Clouds with rain, snow with wind,

429
00:20:22,880 --> 00:20:24,830
and sunset glow with clear sky.

430
00:20:25,510 --> 00:20:27,270
Arriving geese with departing swallows,

431
00:20:28,030 --> 00:20:29,830
resting birds with chirping insects.

432
00:20:30,720 --> 00:20:35,070
Three‑foot sword, six‑stone bow...

433
00:20:36,480 --> 00:20:38,000
Just like when your mom was little,

434
00:20:38,590 --> 00:20:40,110
you forget everything at this part.

435
00:20:40,920 --> 00:20:41,750
Northern mountains...

436
00:20:43,000 --> 00:20:44,480
Northern mountains
with the eastern river.

437
00:20:46,240 --> 00:20:47,200
Mommy!

438
00:20:47,590 --> 00:20:48,510
Mommy,

439
00:20:48,880 --> 00:20:49,480
look!

440
00:20:49,480 --> 00:20:51,880
I wrote all these!

441
00:20:52,070 --> 00:20:53,000
Let me take a look.

442
00:20:54,270 --> 00:20:55,240
Very well written!

443
00:20:55,920 --> 00:20:56,790
You write better than

444
00:20:57,000 --> 00:20:57,750
I did back then.

445
00:20:57,960 --> 00:21:00,240
Grandpa, Mommy praised me!

446
00:21:00,350 --> 00:21:01,920
Yes, Miao worked very hard.

447
00:21:02,550 --> 00:21:03,110
Tell me,

448
00:21:03,400 --> 00:21:04,480
did you make Grandpa angry?

449
00:21:04,720 --> 00:21:05,350
No.

450
00:21:05,920 --> 00:21:06,720
Miao and I

451
00:21:06,960 --> 00:21:08,310
are working together very well.

452
00:21:08,550 --> 00:21:09,550
Am I right, Miao?

453
00:21:11,510 --> 00:21:12,110
Dad,

454
00:21:12,680 --> 00:21:13,310
you've done great.

455
00:21:13,920 --> 00:21:14,550
Thank you.

456
00:21:15,070 --> 00:21:15,960
Don't say that.

457
00:21:17,030 --> 00:21:18,110
I enjoy such wonderful

458
00:21:18,790 --> 00:21:20,480
family life every day.

459
00:21:21,160 --> 00:21:22,350
I must thank you instead.

460
00:21:24,160 --> 00:21:24,960
I congratulate you.

461
00:21:25,510 --> 00:21:26,920
Your company went public.

462
00:21:27,960 --> 00:21:29,200
I saw the news

463
00:21:29,350 --> 00:21:30,200
about your speech

464
00:21:30,880 --> 00:21:32,070
in the listing hall.

465
00:21:32,480 --> 00:21:33,270
It was great.

466
00:21:33,750 --> 00:21:34,920
I'm proud of you.

467
00:21:37,270 --> 00:21:38,400
There's something else.

468
00:21:39,110 --> 00:21:41,200
The TV station told me they wanted

469
00:21:41,750 --> 00:21:42,880
to interview the first

470
00:21:43,160 --> 00:21:43,750
entrepreneur

471
00:21:44,000 --> 00:21:45,920
from Yu County to take a company public,

472
00:21:47,000 --> 00:21:47,960
and I agreed.

473
00:21:48,680 --> 00:21:50,000
Please do it for my sake.

474
00:21:50,350 --> 00:21:51,350
Of course.

475
00:21:52,240 --> 00:21:53,240
But you must promise to go

476
00:21:54,110 --> 00:21:55,160
back to Shenzhen with me.

477
00:21:57,160 --> 00:21:57,830
Miao,

478
00:21:58,550 --> 00:21:59,750
let's bring Grandpa home with us,

479
00:21:59,960 --> 00:22:00,510
okay?

480
00:22:00,510 --> 00:22:01,110
Okay!

481
00:22:02,720 --> 00:22:03,400
You see?

482
00:22:04,070 --> 00:22:05,590
Miao invited me.

483
00:22:06,400 --> 00:22:07,480
I'm very happy.

484
00:22:08,350 --> 00:22:09,350
However,

485
00:22:10,270 --> 00:22:11,750
there's still one thing.

486
00:22:12,920 --> 00:22:13,550
Wanzhi,

487
00:22:14,160 --> 00:22:15,000
come with me.

488
00:22:15,830 --> 00:22:16,480
Come on.

489
00:22:25,070 --> 00:22:26,350
Now that I have time,

490
00:22:27,720 --> 00:22:29,000
I want to finish it

491
00:22:30,000 --> 00:22:30,960
quietly on my own.

492
00:22:32,350 --> 00:22:33,720
The Great Biography of Su Dongpo?

493
00:22:34,000 --> 00:22:34,550
Yes.

494
00:22:35,160 --> 00:22:36,790
Many people have
written about Su Dongpo,

495
00:22:37,830 --> 00:22:39,350
mostly literary scholars.

496
00:22:40,750 --> 00:22:41,640
I'm no more

497
00:22:42,200 --> 00:22:43,920
than an average amateur.

498
00:22:45,070 --> 00:22:46,160
It's been difficult.

499
00:22:47,550 --> 00:22:48,880
But I don't want to give up.

500
00:22:50,830 --> 00:22:51,590
Actually,

501
00:22:52,310 --> 00:22:53,550
it isn't for publication.

502
00:22:54,030 --> 00:22:55,270
It's simply because I love

503
00:22:55,640 --> 00:22:57,400
that sense of boldness
and unconstrained freedom

504
00:22:57,720 --> 00:22:59,240
hailing from a thousand years ago.

505
00:23:06,440 --> 00:23:08,110
Sweetie,

506
00:23:08,750 --> 00:23:10,400
did you miss me?

507
00:23:10,400 --> 00:23:11,480
Did you miss me?

508
00:23:11,590 --> 00:23:12,790
- Say you miss me!
- Be gentle!

509
00:23:12,880 --> 00:23:14,790
You might drop the baby!

510
00:23:15,920 --> 00:23:16,790
Ignore her.

511
00:23:16,960 --> 00:23:17,920
Buzzkill.

512
00:23:19,790 --> 00:23:21,510
Here, let me give you a big kiss!

513
00:23:21,550 --> 00:23:22,400
Kiss kiss!

514
00:23:23,200 --> 00:23:23,960
So nice.

515
00:23:25,000 --> 00:23:26,480
Auntie Juan, I want your kiss.

516
00:23:26,750 --> 00:23:28,070
Oh, okay! Let me kiss you!

517
00:23:30,400 --> 00:23:31,110
Did you like that?

518
00:23:31,440 --> 00:23:32,790
Hey, you see this?

519
00:23:33,200 --> 00:23:35,680
Miao is much more sensible than you.

520
00:23:36,400 --> 00:23:37,680
She's quite a smart kid.

521
00:23:38,310 --> 00:23:39,400
Look how much

522
00:23:39,440 --> 00:23:40,510
she's grown

523
00:23:40,550 --> 00:23:41,640
in just four months!

524
00:23:41,880 --> 00:23:43,350
Why are you so well‑behaved?

525
00:23:43,590 --> 00:23:44,350
I know.

526
00:23:44,640 --> 00:23:46,160
It must be Vice Mayor Meng's credit.

527
00:23:47,680 --> 00:23:48,960
If my son Dahu had such

528
00:23:49,000 --> 00:23:49,880
a good grandfather,

529
00:23:49,960 --> 00:23:51,350
he'd be even more outstanding.

530
00:23:51,640 --> 00:23:52,880
Dahu must have graduated, right?

531
00:23:53,160 --> 00:23:54,030
He has.

532
00:23:56,110 --> 00:23:57,400
He's been hoping to meet you

533
00:23:57,720 --> 00:23:58,550
and asked me to help.

534
00:23:59,030 --> 00:24:00,200
No need for such formality.

535
00:24:00,550 --> 00:24:01,640
He can come here this weekend.

536
00:24:01,960 --> 00:24:03,440
He wants to see you in the office.

537
00:24:03,920 --> 00:24:05,200
Because he's not coming alone.

538
00:24:06,270 --> 00:24:07,400
He's bringing his whole team.

539
00:24:16,680 --> 00:24:17,440
Hello, Ms. Fang.

540
00:24:18,160 --> 00:24:18,640
This is

541
00:24:18,880 --> 00:24:19,920
the founder of Meow Meow Toys,

542
00:24:20,110 --> 00:24:20,720
Fang Wanzhi.

543
00:24:21,200 --> 00:24:21,920
Hello, Ms. Fang.

544
00:24:22,350 --> 00:24:23,750
Please have a seat.

545
00:24:27,310 --> 00:24:27,920
Dahu,

546
00:24:28,510 --> 00:24:29,640
please introduce your team.

547
00:24:30,270 --> 00:24:30,830
Okay.

548
00:24:31,160 --> 00:24:31,880
I'll go first.

549
00:24:32,240 --> 00:24:32,880
Liu Dahu, graduated

550
00:24:33,200 --> 00:24:34,240
from Hong Kong University.

551
00:24:35,240 --> 00:24:35,640
This one,

552
00:24:35,880 --> 00:24:36,480
Tony Tang.

553
00:24:36,790 --> 00:24:37,640
He was my classmate

554
00:24:37,830 --> 00:24:38,550
in Shenzhen.

555
00:24:38,880 --> 00:24:39,550
He later went

556
00:24:39,830 --> 00:24:40,790
to study in the US.

557
00:24:41,160 --> 00:24:41,790
Tony?

558
00:24:42,160 --> 00:24:42,720
This is Peter,

559
00:24:43,000 --> 00:24:43,750
Hua Xiaojie.

560
00:24:43,960 --> 00:24:44,960
My high school classmate.

561
00:24:45,440 --> 00:24:47,000
I completed my bachelor's
studies in China

562
00:24:47,240 --> 00:24:48,400
and graduate studies at Harvard.

563
00:24:48,680 --> 00:24:49,270
And this one

564
00:24:49,270 --> 00:24:50,790
is my senior, Guo Shiqing.

565
00:24:50,920 --> 00:24:51,590
We share

566
00:24:51,680 --> 00:24:52,510
the same mentor.

567
00:24:52,830 --> 00:24:54,510
But she has a PhD.

568
00:24:55,920 --> 00:24:57,510
Dr. Guo, what is your research area?

569
00:24:58,110 --> 00:24:59,590
Just call me Shiqing.

570
00:25:00,030 --> 00:25:01,680
I majored in Electronic Engineering,

571
00:25:02,030 --> 00:25:03,400
and I also hold a PhD

572
00:25:03,480 --> 00:25:04,310
in Education.

573
00:25:04,750 --> 00:25:05,550
Double PhD!

574
00:25:06,310 --> 00:25:06,880
Ms. Fang,

575
00:25:06,880 --> 00:25:07,590
here's a brief.

576
00:25:07,920 --> 00:25:08,830
The four of us met

577
00:25:08,920 --> 00:25:09,880
at an AI forum

578
00:25:09,920 --> 00:25:10,640
in Singapore

579
00:25:10,680 --> 00:25:11,240
last year.

580
00:25:11,400 --> 00:25:12,960
We all wanted to start
a business in Shenzhen,

581
00:25:13,350 --> 00:25:14,590
so we formed this team.

582
00:25:15,200 --> 00:25:16,310
Do you have a direction

583
00:25:16,750 --> 00:25:17,640
for your startup now?

584
00:25:17,750 --> 00:25:19,070
Most current AI applications

585
00:25:19,160 --> 00:25:19,960
are too ambitious.

586
00:25:20,240 --> 00:25:22,240
Defense, healthcare,
autonomous driving...

587
00:25:22,440 --> 00:25:23,480
They're too difficult for us.

588
00:25:23,750 --> 00:25:24,440
Therefore,

589
00:25:24,830 --> 00:25:26,310
we want to start small.

590
00:25:26,720 --> 00:25:27,270
